The paper deals with building an intelligent tutoring system using machine learning techniques to grade short student answers. This involves natural language processing and domain adaptation, which are common topics in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and deep learning (cs.DL). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
